wmii-session

deps
====
wmii, vim, tabbed, surf, zathura, urxvt
task (taskwarrior.org), surfraw


install
=======
copy session.sh to ~/.wmii
copy openurl, openpdf and wmii-session to PATH
mkdir -p $XDG_DATA_HOME/sessions

and you may copy *.desktop to $XDG_DATA_HOME/applications


config (optional)
=================
- in your shell rc:
export $BROWSER='openurl'
alias vim='vim --servername "$(wmiir cat /tag/sel/ctl | sed '1q')"'

- you can set the mime types:
xdg-mime default openurl.desktop application/xhtml_xml
xdg-mime default openurl.desktop text/html
xdg-mime default openurl.desktop text/xml
xdg-mime default openpdf.desktop application/pdf

or just run the commands directly


usage
=====
run "wmii-session help"
or try the sample wmiirc_local


notes
=====
addpath works only from cli:
run "wmii-session addpath" to add $(pwd) to the current tag

task and surfraw are optional,
they add offtopic functionality


